      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLAMING RONDA (6) led them up prior to the break and was bumped into a good winner, beaten 2L. Her trial this time in was very good at Belmont and this looks to shape nicely from the inside draw. Can sit handy in the run and she'll take plenty of beating if she can run up to her recent trial. TRIPLE AR (2) is on debut today for Allan Hughes stable on his home deck. He's been with the Fenella Martin barn to begin his career, trialling nicely at Belmont most recently behind a well-backed commodity in metropolitan grade. That trial form looks to stack up and he can make an immediate impact. SNEAKY SESSION (7) disappointed last time out but was in better touch prior when only 1.4L off the winner. Faithfull hops on board now and a much-improved effort is on the cards. LOONA DAWN (4) just missed at Dongara over the weekend and can feature on the back of that performance. DIXIE PRINCESS (3) is next best.",
